name: UMetaSoundSource
doc: This Metasound type can be played as an audio source.

OutputFormat: The output audio format of the metasound source.
QualitySetting: The Quality this Metasound will use. These are defined in the MetaSounds project settings.
BlockRateOverride: Override the BlockRate for this Sound (overrides Quality). NOTE: A Zero value will have no effect and use either the Quality setting (if set), or the defaults.
SampleRateOverride: Override the SampleRate for this Sound (overrides Quality). NOTE: A Zero value will have no effect and use either the Quality setting (if set), or the Device Rate
